title: [Wraithenmist, Crooked Fork]
description: The faint trail branches off in three directions, each leading back into the thick forest, from this small clearing.  A single spot of sky is visible through a break in the trees directly above, allowing a narrow shaft of moonlight to penetrate the clearing.
